{"tid":1782344,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"（緊急！！！）吾好俾教育局打壓中學生","createTime":"2019-12-14T01:25:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-14T14:35:27.000Z","uid":236894,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"383d7fb347138d26a708f7085f1d994998e3da1d","tid":1782344,"uid":236894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T01:25:53.000Z","msg":"(已FC 麻煩推上熱門)中學校內抗爭將會被全面打壓！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1782087\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1782087</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n回應返以上post<br />\n小妹係某官立中學f5學生 <br />\n因為小妹掛個連儂而被記缺點<br />\n我想請大家幫下班中學生好冇<br />\n我哋被人打壓到很嚴重<br />\n成日話齊上齊落<br />\n我哋班中學生有事<br />\n求下咁多位手足<br />\n搞遊行又好 點都好<br />\n幫下我地<br />\n <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>冇一個中學生想自己被打壓</strong></span><br />\n利申：附上缺點一張和當時的連儂牆 <br />\n如果吾信小妹 小妹都冇辦法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5AmBDJ8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5AmBDJ8.jpg&h=a8cc7d6c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0YR6gvP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0YR6gvP.jpg&h=854cdea9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"110e8de095839aaff86c26609a7652785c2a980e","tid":1782344,"uid":191145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T01:27:38.000Z","msg":"幫推<br />\n<br />\n教育界好快淪陷<br />\n［教育界被清算了］追究發放煽動仇恨言論老師<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1772176\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1772176</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"9eab9e40faf50f86e2adf99694cb210a70f78a17","tid":1782344,"uid":236894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T01:30:10.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"533479b7d3874bf4a4b3081111f3a4f14e198cb6","tid":1782344,"uid":236894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T01:31:36.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"76d9ada3003baa1abb53efbbd4ae1ef39ccd7491","tid":1782344,"uid":235875,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T01:36:15.000Z","msg":"記缺點其實好小事，將來工作唔會睇你缺點，不過亦都唔可以助長教育局氣燄。開學校名，同老師名等我哋放大佢同你搞，一定要求政治議題融入社區。"},{"pid":"1d22109ee28e95f61c9d77079b4a413cdc848e62","tid":1782344,"uid":163704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T01:37:10.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n[你今日FC咗未] 全港最大的Fact Check平台已經推出了<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1776631\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1776631</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"1fd36a48ce7b44e291ac9d0c943e253c7a6be888","tid":1782344,"uid":146285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T01:55:54.000Z","msg":"識記者朋友既人，可以推埋比立場同蘋果，要佢地幫手報出黎先得<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48107b042deb45d60017566f71fbfe561fa38ff5","tid":1782344,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T01:56:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fdf1aa38dcb0e85466b4402509c332cfb242701","tid":1782344,"uid":342828,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T02:09:34.000Z","msg":"請提出證據，及指出是哪一間學校。<br />\n如查明屬實，該校的管理層（包括校董會成員）全部都應該被加入民主與人權法案的制裁名單之內。<br />\n教育局故然是罪魁禍首，但學校管理層若完全配合，不為公義發聲，不為同學爭取，則已成幫兇。<br />\n在這裡奉勸各位仍有良知的教育工作者及協助學校管理工作的校董會成員，若仍不起來，集合眾人之力反抗這個不義的政權，日子只會變得更差，你們亦愧為人師。他日被國際社會制裁，也是疚由自取。"},{"pid":"243db650de162ef0f214bcdc8b8362a50d8fd532","tid":1782344,"uid":196924,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T02:10:24.000Z","msg":"Agger <br />\nBut<br />\n吾你老母"},{"pid":"e12eaef9110227b92815fa6f6cf7c47a2fa35d0f","tid":1782344,"uid":196536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T02:26:10.000Z","msg":"睇黎下次遊行要以呢個為主題<br />\n等全世界都知<br />\n中共維穩統戰之心不死